    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses intense emotional distress, feelings of being a burden, and a desire to \"let go\" to escape overwhelming pressure. The assistant attempts to provide empathetic support by validating the user's feelings of being at a breaking point while simultaneously urging them to seek help and take breaks.",
